}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== <small>This device is likely an evolution of the [[ASUS GT-AX6000]]/[[ASUS GT-AC5400]] development devices with an upgraded CPU. Many details for this device have been copied from the pages for those devices and are subject to change. Photos of pre-production devices show the RT-AX89X reusing the FCC id from the GT-AX6000 and ASUS will probably eventually issue a Class II Product Change Request for that ID to certify the RT-AX89X.</small>
